DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260712
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260713
SUMMARY:🥾 J05 - Yosemite Valley (Mist Trail) → Bass Lake
DESCRIPTION:06h30 Départ Sweetwater → Yosemite Valley (Tunnel View en chemin)\n07h30 Parking Upper Pines\n07h45 Navette → Happy Isles\n07h45-12h00 Mist Trail : Vernal Fall + Nevada Fall (12\,8 km\, 815m D+\, ~5h30)\n12h45 Navette → El Capitan Meadow\n13h00-14h00 El Capitan (vue paroi 900m\, grimpeurs)\n14h15-15h30 Yosemite Falls (Lower Yosemite Fall Trail 1\,6 km)\n16h00 Route Yosemite → Bass Lake (~80-100 km\, 1h30-2h)\n18h30 Check-in Oh Ridge Campground - site 141 (Deer)\n🏕️ Oh Ridge Campground - Bass Lake - conf. reservation-camping-12-07.pdf
